31.01.2007 AK SCR12100 fixed bug in task 'outstanding invo statistics'

SQL_STMT_U.val:
SELECT INVO_DEBC_NO, INVO_NO, INVO_INVOICENO, INVO_INVDATE, INVO_DUEDATE, INVO_CURRENCY, INVO_AINITIALC, INVO_AINITIALI, cast(ifnull(INVO_AINITIALC - ( select sum(BPIV_AMOUNTCURRC) from :1/BPIV where BPIV_INVO_NO=INVO_NO and BPIV_CASHREPORTDATE<=':3' ),INVO_AINITIALC )as decimal(13,2) ) as REPACTUALC, cast(ifnull(INVO_AINITIALI - ( select sum(BPIV_AMOUNTCURRINV) from :1/BPIV where BPIV_INVO_NO=INVO_NO and BPIV_CASHREPORTDATE<=':3' ),INVO_AINITIALI )as decimal(13,2) ) as REPACTUALINV
FROM :1/INVO
WHERE INVO_INVDATE<= ':3' and INVO_DEBC_NO = :2 and cast(ifnull(INVO_AINITIALC - ( select sum(BPIV_AMOUNTCURRC) from :1/BPIV where BPIV_INVO_NO=INVO_NO and BPIV_CASHREPORTDATE<=':3' ),INVO_AINITIALC )as decimal(13,2) ) <>0
ORDER BY INVO_INVDATE,INVO_INVOICENO
